                        <p rend="flushleft">Subject: Division of German Naval Vessels.</p>
                        <p rend="flushleft">Reference: <hi rend="italic">a</hi>. SWNCC 208/10.<note n="59" xml:id="d1150fn59">Not printed.</note>
                        </p>
                        <p>The State-War-Navy Coordinating Committee has approved, on behalf of the
                            United States Government, the division of German naval <pb facs="1530" n="1520" xml:id="pg_1520"/> vessels as outlined in reference <hi rend="italic">a</hi>. The division of these vessels is as
                            follows:</p>
