                        <p>It is requested that the United States Member of the Tripartite Naval
                            Commission notify the United Kingdom and the Union of Soviet Socialist
                            Republics Member of the Commission of the approval <pb facs="1531" n="1521" xml:id="pg_1521"/> by the United States Government of the
                            division of German vessels set forth above.</p>
                        <p>For the State-War-Navy Coordinating Committee:</p>
                        <closer>
